body:
The necessary changes for the Digitizer to read inefficiency factors from DataBase. The factors which are read from the DB are the same as previously read from python files (which are now commented out).
For the Phase1 detector there is only trivial efficiency loss included therefor there is no payload for it, those factors are still set from the  SLHCUpgradeSimulations package.

@diguida @mmusich you've asked to review this PR.
